{"tid":922030,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"飲食聽con懶up圖：首爾四日 (17-20 Nov 2018)","createTime":"2018-11-30T04:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T06:34:52.000Z","uid":68876,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"87a283b67a86f4fd6088b5a44817f52b67ff38bb","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"為聽con而去首爾，三年前試過一次，朝早去夜晚con第朝就返，勁撻皮；今次又去，好在有假，所以順手飲飲食食，順便幫屋企人帶貨。不過飲乜食乜同買乜，就未必係大路嘢咁易估；亦同埋啲例牌上機落機影燈版影飛機餐嘅都skip晒，費事嘥大家啲RAM去load。Anyway here we go...<br />\n<br />\n17 Nov - KE612<br />\n收工返屋企，食埋嘢沖埋涼飛red-eye，點都係咁最抵玩；落機啱啱天光，搭埋AREX出去，去到明洞啱啱九點鬆啲，食碗粥就過酒店擺低嘢，然後仆返出去辦貨...<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1110001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1110001.jpg&h=65b7e97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114111.jpg&h=2dd7e584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114251.jpg&h=9b0c0f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辦貨地方係三清洞，行開就是是但拍幾張；辦咩貨？之後再講。<br />\n<br />\n辦完貨，搭地鐵去到新沙洞食晏嘅地方。搵得兩搵，啱啱好：<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00011.jpg&h=8918e6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1315041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1315041.jpg&h=2950a17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間嘢叫Ryunique (<a href=\"http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ryunique.co.kr%2Fmain&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=38c71555\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main</a>)，整嘅係現代西餐，用本地材料。個廚響歐洲同日本都學過師，個人覺得整海產係有返兩道散手。唔講太多，嘢食圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1201521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1201521.jpg&h=4a89f5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壓扁嘅香魚 (ayu)，整成脆片<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00051.jpg&h=d4f4b7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓豬火腿蘋果無花果青瓜沙律，清爽<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219431.jpg&h=9356278f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219461.jpg&h=d9c162c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人蔘野菌黑雞清湯；零零仃仃嗰嚿係煙燻蜜餞人蔘包黑雞髀肉，跟湯食。個湯雞味鮮濃，而且好清澈，隔油隔得好盡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1230201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1230201.jpg&h=30b3cb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n土產鱈魚拼鮟鱇魚肝，汁係藍蟹海鮮hollandaise。魚肝極出色：鮮、滑，唔腥，而汁底嘅蔬果成分畫龍點睛，同啲海產味撞開個contrast幾sharp醒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1239381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1239381.jpg&h=1fe43cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n濟洲橙冰沙+橙汁波，清下味蕾<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1252051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1252051.jpg&h=c9804244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑松露配薑檸蜜燒汁鵪鶉三食(肉丸+髀肉medallion+包咗蘿蔔上芝麻嘅炸髀)，side係洋蔥、人蔘薯泥同菜沙律<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1303451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1303451.jpg&h=44d0936b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1312461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1312461.jpg&h=27763c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n甜品 (朱古力蛋糕跟紅莓雪葩、棉花糖、黃豆粉、綠茶糖膠)同petit four<br />\n<br />\n正午食到差唔多兩點，夠鐘返明洞去酒店攞房。攞完房跟手再出去...<br />\n<br />\n[TBC]~"},{"pid":"c4fca1f39982897e146c779f84c218fb2f33638b","tid":922030,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"聽邊個嘅演唱會？"},{"pid":"65d02ee16ad0ee88184406476861b1ee94a26505","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4fca1f39982897e146c779f84c218fb2f33638b","tid":922030,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"聽邊個嘅演唱會？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"IU，18 Nov 嗰場~"},{"pid":"34a830d28c231941ed83d8e72f0bab8e5eed53df","tid":922030,"uid":76632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"65d02ee16ad0ee88184406476861b1ee94a26505","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4fca1f39982897e146c779f84c218fb2f33638b","tid":922030,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"聽邊個嘅演唱會？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"IU，18 Nov 嗰場~"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名支持"},{"pid":"5ad84baf764eac24dec8129a54e68eb3b24d12bd","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"17 Nov 2018 - pm and dinner<br />\n攞咗放再爆完石，都已經唔早(三點幾四點)，即刻又撲出去，目的地係合井。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1630391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1630391.jpg&h=b36b7ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1649061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1649061.jpg&h=8830df3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n匆匆忙忙，是是但鳩拍兩張。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00131.jpg&h=482ca519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果乾pound cake+手沖啡(薩爾瓦多)@Manufact Coffee Roasters<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1733571.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1733571.jpg&h=32c368b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCafe外貌<br />\n<br />\n搞完一輪，六點幾，即刻仆去新羅；擒擒青響大堂Library Lounge飲咗杯人蔘汁+鮮奶+蜜糖，夠鐘就上去羅宴食韓菜&mdash;今次出門嘅highlight之一。<br />\n餐廳資料：<a href=\"https://www.shilla.net/seoul/dining/viewDining.do?contId=KRN#ad-image-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shilla.net%2Fseoul%2Fdining%2FviewDining.do%3FcontId%3DKRN%23ad-image-0&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a687c033\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shilla.net/seoul/dining/viewDining.do?contId=KRN#ad-image-0</a><br />\n廢話少講，開餐：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4GfPcZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4GfPcZ.jpg&h=d55040b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n栗茸奶湯；比想像中清，但栗子味好足。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1928241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1928241.jpg&h=abf08892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九色前菜<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1933531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1933531.jpg&h=95c93509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生帶子配柚子醬油啫喱及椰菜；生帶子同埋個啫喱、啲菜要一齊啪入口，味道鮮甜清爽，層次分明。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1938261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1938261.jpg&h=1ea3ec7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蟹肉松子羹；真係未試過嘅配搭，蟹肉當然鮮味，配松子羹質地出奇咁夾，而松子獨有嘅香味令成個feel「高級」咗，唔俗氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1949231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1949231.jpg&h=e1229f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n覆盆子五味子汁煎鴨胸；本地化嘅汁，雖然都係酸酸甜甜嘅果味，但同平日食開嘅紅莓藍莓之類汁底係好唔同，別有風味。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1954171.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1954171.jpg&h=07c8741c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火鍋；蛋同魚片最正，蔬菜爽口，整體味道係偏向清嗰路(不過牛肉清湯底都夠味)，食完都無點影響戰力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2007561.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2007561.jpg&h=e3edfe07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓牛菜式三揀一，揀咗醬油煮牛肋骨(入面有栗子、洋蔥同淮山)，貪佢多少少廚功見到。牛肉本身質素唔使多講，個汁底味道輕身過平日響一般韓菜食店食到嗰啲，鹹甜平衡，而甜味來自蔬菜配料嘅比例亦多啲，唔錯唔錯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2022161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2022161.jpg&h=776a6ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主食，揀咗白飯跟牛肋骨鮑魚湯。湯底清澈鮮甜，鮑魚亦鮮味，雖然已經飽到八八九，照樣殺晒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2045061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2045061.jpg&h=5eaeb7fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n甜品：栗茸燉蛋、榛子雪糕配紅蔘黑糖漿。冬天feel，紅蔘糖漿個味好醒神。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2051301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2051301.jpg&h=edff4a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埋尾：黑糖薑茶、棗泥糕<br />\n<br />\n食呢餐同日頭一樣，都有飲酒(日頭餐係香檳by glass，2007 Laurent Perrier Brut)，呢餐就飲咗韓式米酒。酒色金黃，味香甜，同《倚天屠龍記》入面苦頭陀搵嚟陰鳩鶴筆翁嗰隻幾似。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAnyway，七點食到九點，飽晒，嗱嗱聲找數，再趕去飲嘢...<br />\n[TBC]"},{"pid":"1bcbcee7e3dab25e58611a34180a872a5842cd07","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"高汁留名<br />\n一餐幾錢左右"},{"pid":"9a31f81e1de1c1d71188e7ce7331245a02564ee6","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1bcbcee7e3dab25e58611a34180a872a5842cd07","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"高汁留名<br />\n一餐幾錢左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"多謝讚賞~<br />\n<br />\n日頭個西餐，唔計酒水，基本價12萬won，再加一，折返港紙$900左右。晚黑羅宴嗰餐就貴嘅，唔計酒水，基本價再加一就大約30萬won (我揀貴／多啲嘢食個set)，折港紙大約 $2,100。<br />\n<br />\n想試羅宴又唔想太肉赤嘅，可以試下日頭去；嘢食當然少啲，但又唔使食到咁飽，平set連加一無酒水大約係11.5萬won，港紙八嚿左右，可以一戰。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131b3156dd4ba388c913db50d6194dd2f90a7b10","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a31f81e1de1c1d71188e7ce7331245a02564ee6","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1bcbcee7e3dab25e58611a34180a872a5842cd07","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"高汁留名<br />\n一餐幾錢左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"多謝讚賞~<br />\n<br />\n日頭個西餐，唔計酒水，基本價12萬won，再加一，折返港紙$900左右。晚黑羅宴嗰餐就貴嘅，唔計酒水，基本價再加一就大約30萬won (我揀貴／多啲嘢食個set)，折港紙大約 $2,100。<br />\n<br />\n想試羅宴又唔想太肉赤嘅，可以試下日頭去；嘢食當然少啲，但又唔使食到咁飽，平set連加一無酒水大約係11.5萬won，港紙八嚿左右，可以一戰。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"我自己ok<br />\n但我啲朋友實唔肯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主有冇三四百嘅韓牛推薦<br />\n<br />\nBtw 勿爛尾"},{"pid":"8f4707a9cf48674b9ec37037545dd7f7b76ed23b","tid":922030,"uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:33:25.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1ab7f82259270fae243cb90e2a77c74d4e5ae0","tid":922030,"uid":127039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"Shit place<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12494e28930d5614b6dfdb57788029013fd547d","tid":922030,"uid":63177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"推。 貴價韓遊<br />\n終於有非窮遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d198a33773856d587edf3f2f0983d8cffc4d56d","tid":922030,"uid":198780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為聽con而去首爾，三年前試過一次，朝早去夜晚con第朝就返，勁撻皮；今次又去，好在有假，所以順手飲飲食食，順便幫屋企人帶貨。不過飲乜食乜同買乜，就未必係大路嘢咁易估；亦同埋啲例牌上機落機影燈版影飛機餐嘅都skip晒，費事嘥大家啲RAM去load。Anyway here we go...<br />\n<br />\n17 Nov - KE612<br />\n收工返屋企，食埋嘢沖埋涼飛red-eye，點都係咁最抵玩；落機啱啱天光，搭埋AREX出去，去到明洞啱啱九點鬆啲，食碗粥就過酒店擺低嘢，然後仆返出去辦貨...<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1110001.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1110001.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=461a1852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1110001.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114111.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114111.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f83d248e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114111.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114251.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114251.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b3841290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114251.jpg[/im</a><br />\n辦貨地方係三，行開就是是但拍幾張；辦咩貨？之後再講。<br />\n<br />\n辦完貨，搭地鐵去到新沙洞食晏嘅地方。搵得兩搵，啱啱好：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00011.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00011.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=69e287a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00011.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1315041.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1315041.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=564e5ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1315041.jpg[/im</a><br />\n間嘢叫Ryunique (<a href=\"http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ryunique.co.kr%2Fmain&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=38c71555\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main</a>)，整嘅係現代西餐，用本地材料。個廚響歐洲同日本都學過師，個人覺得整海產係有返兩道散手。唔講太多，嘢食圖：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1201521.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1201521.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=72daf661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1201521.jpg[/im</a><br />\n壓扁嘅香魚 (ayu)，整成脆片<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00051.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00051.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=998fbfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00051.jpg[/im</a><br />\n韓豬火腿蘋果無花果青瓜沙律，清爽<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219431.jpg[/im[img]https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219461.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219431.jpg%5B%2Fim%5Bimg%5Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219461.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=74cc5256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219431.jpg[/im[img]https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219461.jpg[/im</a><br />\n人蔘野菌黑雞清湯；零零仃仃嗰嚿係煙燻蜜餞人蔘包黑雞髀肉，跟湯食。個湯雞味鮮濃，而且好清澈，隔油隔得好盡。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1230201.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1230201.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6e45af1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1230201.jpg[/im</a><br />\n土產鱈魚拼鮟鱇魚肝，汁係藍蟹海鮮hollandaise。魚肝極出色：鮮、滑，唔腥，而汁底嘅蔬果成分畫龍點睛，同啲海產味撞開個contrast幾sharp醒。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1239381.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1239381.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=16583907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1239381.jpg[/im</a><br />\n濟洲橙冰沙+橙汁波，清下味蕾<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1252051.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1252051.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9f7f20ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1252051.jpg[/im</a><br />\n黑松露配薑檸蜜燒汁鵪鶉三食(肉丸+髀肉medallion+包咗蘿蔔上芝麻嘅炸髀)，side係洋蔥、人蔘薯泥同菜沙律<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1303451.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1303451.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cc7f2007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1303451.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1312461.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1312461.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a428f302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1312461.jpg[/im</a><br />\n甜品 (朱古力蛋糕跟紅莓雪葩、棉花糖、黃豆粉、綠茶糖膠)同petit four<br />\n<br />\n正午食到差唔多兩點，夠鐘返明洞去酒店攞房。攞完房跟手再出去...<br />\n<br />\n[TBC]~</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f59b10d2e764d273eb14b77f74d2900dcba0a9a5","tid":922030,"uid":198780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d198a33773856d587edf3f2f0983d8cffc4d56d","tid":922030,"uid":198780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為聽con而去首爾，三年前試過一次，朝早去夜晚con第朝就返，勁撻皮；今次又去，好在有假，所以順手飲飲食食，順便幫屋企人帶貨。不過飲乜食乜同買乜，就未必係大路嘢咁易估；亦同埋啲例牌上機落機影燈版影飛機餐嘅都skip晒，費事嘥大家啲RAM去load。Anyway here we go...<br />\n<br />\n17 Nov - KE612<br />\n收工返屋企，食埋嘢沖埋涼飛red-eye，點都係咁最抵玩；落機啱啱天光，搭埋AREX出去，去到明洞啱啱九點鬆啲，食碗粥就過酒店擺低嘢，然後仆返出去辦貨...<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1110001.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1110001.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=461a1852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1110001.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114111.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114111.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f83d248e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114111.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114251.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114251.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b3841290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114251.jpg[/im</a><br />\n辦貨地方係三，行開就是是但拍幾張；辦咩貨？之後再講。<br />\n<br />\n辦完貨，搭地鐵去到新沙洞食晏嘅地方。搵得兩搵，啱啱好：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00011.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00011.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=69e287a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00011.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1315041.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1315041.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=564e5ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1315041.jpg[/im</a><br />\n間嘢叫Ryunique (<a href=\"http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ryunique.co.kr%2Fmain&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=38c71555\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main</a>)，整嘅係現代西餐，用本地材料。個廚響歐洲同日本都學過師，個人覺得整海產係有返兩道散手。唔講太多，嘢食圖：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1201521.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1201521.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=72daf661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1201521.jpg[/im</a><br />\n壓扁嘅香魚 (ayu)，整成脆片<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00051.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00051.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=998fbfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00051.jpg[/im</a><br />\n韓豬火腿蘋果無花果青瓜沙律，清爽<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219431.jpg[/im[img]https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219461.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219431.jpg%5B%2Fim%5Bimg%5Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219461.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=74cc5256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219431.jpg[/im[img]https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219461.jpg[/im</a><br />\n人蔘野菌黑雞清湯；零零仃仃嗰嚿係煙燻蜜餞人蔘包黑雞髀肉，跟湯食。個湯雞味鮮濃，而且好清澈，隔油隔得好盡。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1230201.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1230201.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6e45af1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1230201.jpg[/im</a><br />\n土產鱈魚拼鮟鱇魚肝，汁係藍蟹海鮮hollandaise。魚肝極出色：鮮、滑，唔腥，而汁底嘅蔬果成分畫龍點睛，同啲海產味撞開個contrast幾sharp醒。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1239381.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1239381.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=16583907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1239381.jpg[/im</a><br />\n濟洲橙冰沙+橙汁波，清下味蕾<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1252051.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1252051.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9f7f20ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1252051.jpg[/im</a><br />\n黑松露配薑檸蜜燒汁鵪鶉三食(肉丸+髀肉medallion+包咗蘿蔔上芝麻嘅炸髀)，side係洋蔥、人蔘薯泥同菜沙律<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1303451.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1303451.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cc7f2007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1303451.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1312461.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1312461.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a428f302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1312461.jpg[/im</a><br />\n甜品 (朱古力蛋糕跟紅莓雪葩、棉花糖、黃豆粉、綠茶糖膠)同petit four<br />\n<br />\n正午食到差唔多兩點，夠鐘返明洞去酒店攞房。攞完房跟手再出去...<br />\n<br />\n[TBC]~</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"自膠<br />\n好想去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e1884c1fb40c4ebe465048d14371ed5fb23cf5","tid":922030,"uid":198780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f59b10d2e764d273eb14b77f74d2900dcba0a9a5","tid":922030,"uid":198780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d198a33773856d587edf3f2f0983d8cffc4d56d","tid":922030,"uid":198780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為聽con而去首爾，三年前試過一次，朝早去夜晚con第朝就返，勁撻皮；今次又去，好在有假，所以順手飲飲食食，順便幫屋企人帶貨。不過飲乜食乜同買乜，就未必係大路嘢咁易估；亦同埋啲例牌上機落機影燈版影飛機餐嘅都skip晒，費事嘥大家啲RAM去load。Anyway here we go...<br />\n<br />\n17 Nov - KE612<br />\n收工返屋企，食埋嘢沖埋涼飛red-eye，點都係咁最抵玩；落機啱啱天光，搭埋AREX出去，去到明洞啱啱九點鬆啲，食碗粥就過酒店擺低嘢，然後仆返出去辦貨...<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1110001.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1110001.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=461a1852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1110001.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114111.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114111.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f83d248e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114111.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114251.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1114251.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b3841290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1114251.jpg[/im</a><br />\n辦貨地方係三，行開就是是但拍幾張；辦咩貨？之後再講。<br />\n<br />\n辦完貨，搭地鐵去到新沙洞食晏嘅地方。搵得兩搵，啱啱好：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00011.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00011.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=69e287a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00011.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1315041.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1315041.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=564e5ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1315041.jpg[/im</a><br />\n間嘢叫Ryunique (<a href=\"http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ryunique.co.kr%2Fmain&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=38c71555\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ryunique.co.kr/main</a>)，整嘅係現代西餐，用本地材料。個廚響歐洲同日本都學過師，個人覺得整海產係有返兩道散手。唔講太多，嘢食圖：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1201521.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1201521.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=72daf661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1201521.jpg[/im</a><br />\n壓扁嘅香魚 (ayu)，整成脆片<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00051.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg-20181117-wa00051.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=998fbfaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img-20181117-wa00051.jpg[/im</a><br />\n韓豬火腿蘋果無花果青瓜沙律，清爽<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219431.jpg[/im[img]https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219461.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219431.jpg%5B%2Fim%5Bimg%5Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1219461.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=74cc5256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219431.jpg[/im[img]https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1219461.jpg[/im</a><br />\n人蔘野菌黑雞清湯；零零仃仃嗰嚿係煙燻蜜餞人蔘包黑雞髀肉，跟湯食。個湯雞味鮮濃，而且好清澈，隔油隔得好盡。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1230201.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1230201.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6e45af1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1230201.jpg[/im</a><br />\n土產鱈魚拼鮟鱇魚肝，汁係藍蟹海鮮hollandaise。魚肝極出色：鮮、滑，唔腥，而汁底嘅蔬果成分畫龍點睛，同啲海產味撞開個contrast幾sharp醒。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1239381.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1239381.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=16583907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1239381.jpg[/im</a><br />\n濟洲橙冰沙+橙汁波，清下味蕾<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1252051.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1252051.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9f7f20ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1252051.jpg[/im</a><br />\n黑松露配薑檸蜜燒汁鵪鶉三食(肉丸+髀肉medallion+包咗蘿蔔上芝麻嘅炸髀)，side係洋蔥、人蔘薯泥同菜沙律<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1303451.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1303451.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cc7f2007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1303451.jpg[/im</a><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1312461.jpg[/im\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_1312461.jpg%5B%2Fim&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a428f302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_1312461.jpg[/im</a><br />\n甜品 (朱古力蛋糕跟紅莓雪葩、棉花糖、黃豆粉、綠茶糖膠)同petit four<br />\n<br />\n正午食到差唔多兩點，夠鐘返明洞去酒店攞房。攞完房跟手再出去...<br />\n<br />\n[TBC]~</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"自膠<br />\n好想去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a071b7be90dbfef4d70d1034d2767013c3cfda","tid":922030,"uid":13747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57799696f88c31edd10d110c9e98d33b139874f7","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a071b7be90dbfef4d70d1034d2767013c3cfda","tid":922030,"uid":13747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:26:08.000Z","msg":"Sor，撳錯負皮...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7e9229653eb83be5dd8b309e92209489a28ddb","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"131b3156dd4ba388c913db50d6194dd2f90a7b10","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a31f81e1de1c1d71188e7ce7331245a02564ee6","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1bcbcee7e3dab25e58611a34180a872a5842cd07","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"高汁留名<br />\n一餐幾錢左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"多謝讚賞~<br />\n<br />\n日頭個西餐，唔計酒水，基本價12萬won，再加一，折返港紙$900左右。晚黑羅宴嗰餐就貴嘅，唔計酒水，基本價再加一就大約30萬won (我揀貴／多啲嘢食個set)，折港紙大約 $2,100。<br />\n<br />\n想試羅宴又唔想太肉赤嘅，可以試下日頭去；嘢食當然少啲，但又唔使食到咁飽，平set連加一無酒水大約係11.5萬won，港紙八嚿左右，可以一戰。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"我自己ok<br />\n但我啲朋友實唔肯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主有冇三四百嘅韓牛推薦<br />\n<br />\nBtw 勿爛尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"陣間上第三篇~<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n韓牛燒烤嘅話，今次食咗間幾正嘅，乾淨企理，啲牛直頭擺響好似高級肉食店入面嗰啲凍display櫃咁畀你揀。三種部位拼盤就14500 won/100g，西冷同肉眼就好似23000 won/100g，有得幾個人一齊又唔係太大食嘅話，三四嚿港紙一位應該做到。一陣我掘返個地址出嚟。"},{"pid":"a00bd44085e04d79833dc9d42af99681c6955e59","tid":922030,"uid":17610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0490c33f3a1d4bef965442fe485e866d012b238b","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"131b3156dd4ba388c913db50d6194dd2f90a7b10","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a31f81e1de1c1d71188e7ce7331245a02564ee6","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1bcbcee7e3dab25e58611a34180a872a5842cd07","tid":922030,"uid":41562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T12:33:14.000Z","msg":"高汁留名<br />\n一餐幾錢左右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"多謝讚賞~<br />\n<br />\n日頭個西餐，唔計酒水，基本價12萬won，再加一，折返港紙$900左右。晚黑羅宴嗰餐就貴嘅，唔計酒水，基本價再加一就大約30萬won (我揀貴／多啲嘢食個set)，折港紙大約 $2,100。<br />\n<br />\n想試羅宴又唔想太肉赤嘅，可以試下日頭去；嘢食當然少啲，但又唔使食到咁飽，平set連加一無酒水大約係11.5萬won，港紙八嚿左右，可以一戰。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"我自己ok<br />\n但我啲朋友實唔肯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主有冇三四百嘅韓牛推薦<br />\n<br />\nBtw 勿爛尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b480833c8df7c9b0d4db1aec38b9b7240f596925","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e12494e28930d5614b6dfdb57788029013fd547d","tid":922030,"uid":63177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"推。 貴價韓遊<br />\n終於有非窮遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"客氣客氣；其實都唔完全係貴價，酒店方面住得唔算貴 (Holiday Inn Express)，同埋無點買手信，機票都係用上網同手機消費積分去換~<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b3494eaae7ac71226c073cd4b9f4dfad8de4cc","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"17 Nov - Drinks after dinner<br />\n食完嘢，飽到上心口；趕落去搭地鐵；望兩眼見夜晚酒店都有啲景唔錯，快手影咗幾張：<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2106581.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2106581.jpg&h=373723d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新羅間迎賓館<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2107231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2107231.jpg&h=963079b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2107561.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2107561.jpg&h=3e7b2782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢轉去都重有啲地方見到紅葉，但最靚覺得係夜晚影呢兩張<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2109471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2109471.jpg&h=94b473f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該係酒店嘅聖誕裝飾<br />\n<br />\n跟手衝入地鐵，轉一次車，去到梨泰院。近一兩年開始認真少少飲cocktails，所以今次響網上做咗些少功課，就針住今年Asia Top 50入選嗰幾間，再加兩三間榜外嘅；呢晚原本計劃梨泰院去兩間：第一間叫Blacklist (梨泰院1洞，66-2)，不過搵到去嗰陣爆晒棚，即閃，行多幾步去到綠沙坪，終於有地方飲嘞：<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2228521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2228521.jpg&h=a19e7019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRum-based tiki-drink，(好似)叫Italian Bird。手勢幾好，啲料搖得勻meld得埋，味道無太甜太苦側埋一邊嗰啲，塊燒菠蘿乾(畀我食咗先記得影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )畫龍點睛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2208121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2208121.jpg&h=444e4efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOmija Mule - Vodka-based Moscow Mule嘅變種，用咗五味子乾。別開生面之作，招牌嘢嚟。<br />\n<br />\n間嘢叫Southside Parlor (綠沙坪大路218號4樓)；風格係Texas/Carribean，輕鬆／多人，會嘈啲嗰類。無上Asia Top 50個榜，但啲嘢風評唔錯，呢次試完係幾得。另外同個應該係次席mixologist交流幾句，都有啲料聽到下 (e.g. 心水bar推介)：佢本人鍾意返江北，尤其佢哋梨泰院啲行家架步多啲，因為抵玩好多；；江南嗰頭名店多，啲嘢唔係唔得，不過貴，有部分佢認為太花巧。Anyway，有相，大家如果有機會幫襯嘅可以同佢吹下水 (另外有個男嘅首席mixologist，不過佢忙好多，費事阻人做嘢)：<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-frt3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/5c50bdcc42db1b1c6d8eae4a5ea7668d/5C91E0F6/t51.2885-15/e35/39011800_895511693993365_1991482563134226432_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-frt3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F5c50bdcc42db1b1c6d8eae4a5ea7668d%2F5C91E0F6%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F39011800_895511693993365_1991482563134226432_n.jpg&h=fdb6eb52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係呢位姐姐(網上搵返嘅相；宜家髮型唔同。個名叫Bomin但我嗰陣聽咗做Bomi，應該係畀APink肥波毒到上咗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )；佢都嚟過香港，去過Quinary同Pontiac呢啲大場觀摩，而且同Pontiac都合作過(<a href=\"https://thehoneycombers.com/hong-kong/event/the-pontiac-southside-parlor-takeover/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthehoneycombers.com%2Fhong-kong%2Fevent%2Fthe-pontiac-southside-parlor-takeover%2F&d=%2FdB45soenP09IF%2FK9W4J3dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cf26a928\" target=\"_blank\">https://thehoneycombers.com/hong-kong/event/the-pontiac-southside-parlor-takeover/</a>)，睇第日有無機會又碰頭。<br />\n<br />\n九點十坐到十點九，差唔多成個鐘，又吹咗水，即刻趕地鐵去下場<br />\n<br />\n[TBC]~"},{"pid":"2a5ef6c918c565ce5cf51d09d74231d595d6f468","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"17 Nov - Drinks after dinner, 2nd round<br />\n飲完第一場，嗱嗱聲趕地鐵去光化門Four Seasons；第二場間嘢就響呢度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-D3AOfRU2SwU/VqoM1DpyHPI/AAAAAAAAUv0/xtQ6GHnT4Ig/s1600/DSC01139.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-D3AOfRU2SwU%2FVqoM1DpyHPI%2FAAAAAAAAUv0%2FxtQ6GHnT4Ig%2Fs1600%2FDSC01139.JPG&h=9390b990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張相唔係我自己影嘅，不過各位如果第日撞啱有興趣想試下嘅，呢張相會好有用：間嘢係所謂speakeasy bar，即係上世紀二三十年代美國禁酒令時期，扮鬼扮馬／隱形嚟掩飾嗰種酒吧。大家留意圖入面正中間條柱有個唔係好起眼嘅門柄，開門就係嗰度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n坐低就嗌嘢飲，先後飲咗三杯：<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181117_2342001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181117_2342001.jpg&h=b945b73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n干邑底，但飲落幾light，啱女士飲。響Charles H. Baker (十九至二十世紀嘅旅遊飲食KOL)某本cocktail guidebook拎出嚟嘅recipe。而間嘢個名叫&quot;Charles H.&quot;，亦講明係用呢位仁兄做概念：啲cocktails定期會換，以佢本guidebook入面嘅「地區」做概念分類。之前有一輪出過香港，今期無咗，記得有嘅好似係印度、埃及、美國(NY)同菲律賓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181118_0015331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181118_0015331.jpg&h=08299d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOld Fashioned變種，改rum-based。加重橙皮之後整到似傳統whisky-based嘅效果，幾盞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181118_0048111.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181118_0048111.jpg&h=711d5f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGin-based，重果味。不過全日飲咁多次酒之後，去到Charles H呢輪都已經唔係記得好完整每杯嘢係點，所以可能有嘢記錯，各位唔好見怪。<br />\n<br />\n同場加料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181118_012023_ed1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181118_012023_ed1.jpg&h=a8f17662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事緣係咁：有兩個男嘅bartenders，吹水講開原來都係IU飯，不過佢哋一個無假一個搶唔到飛，所以無得睇con；跟手佢哋就指咗呢位負責帶位嘅姐姐過嚟，話佢係在場職員IU飯3號，而且平日重成日迫佢哋話佢似IU (!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，所以叫咗佢埋嚟影相嘞。不過基於(1)「毒撚最忌有自信」、(2)「唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出嚟柒」嘅原則同埋(3)當時已經半貓，雖然諗返都有啲後悔，都係唔敢抄牌嘞...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飲完嘢吹完水講完笑，都成點鐘，行路趕返酒店 (步行&lt;15 min)；<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181118_0134061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181118_0134061.jpg&h=59aafba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光化門站前十字路口<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/img_20181118_0137461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortmarcy71.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F11%2Fimg_20181118_0137461.jpg&h=c9a33ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清溪川<br />\n<br />\n返到酒店，兩下就攤低，連涼都唔記得沖...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[TBC]~"},{"pid":"c06eb05662c82f4a436db62b4d34e806f3cc2148","tid":922030,"uid":14554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"支持 留名等睇IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222f392fc0cb09d4596ca1ad4ca27f3678dfce12","tid":922030,"uid":63177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"樓主飲咁多杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1ae1b49fa199a943f36bb2412eddac6846c81c","tid":922030,"uid":68876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"222f392fc0cb09d4596ca1ad4ca27f3678dfce12","tid":922030,"uid":63177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"樓主飲咁多杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"其實唔算飲得，純粹爛飲...無趴低響街算好彩。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢兩日忙，睇下今晚上Day 2..."}]}